        self.qldb_driver.execute_lambda(lambda txn: txn.execute_statement(search_query, ion_value_string, COLUMN_NAME, COLUMN_NAME))

We do support pass the value of field as a parameter whereas we don't support table name as a parameter for parameterized statement in the execute statement request.
